[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6505,
        "end_time": 7883,
        "text": "If you&#39;ve had surgery,"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 7883,
        "end_time": 11116,
        "text": "you might remember starting to count\nbackwards from ten,"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 11116,
        "end_time": 12368,
        "text": "nine,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 12368,
        "end_time": 13461,
        "text": "eight,"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 13461,
        "end_time": 18853,
        "text": "and then waking up with the surgery\nalready over before you even got to five."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 18853,
        "end_time": 21968,
        "text": "And it might seem like you were asleep,\nbut you weren&#39;t."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 21968,
        "end_time": 23844,
        "text": "You were under anesthesia,"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 23844,
        "end_time": 25636,
        "text": "which is much more complicated."
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 25636,
        "end_time": 26665,
        "text": "You were unconscious,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 26665,
        "end_time": 28399,
        "text": "but you also couldn&#39;t move,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 28399,
        "end_time": 29622,
        "text": "form memories,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 29622,
        "end_time": 32225,
        "text": "or, hopefully, feel pain."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 32225,
        "end_time": 35180,
        "text": "Without being able to block all those\nprocesses at once,"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 35180,
        "end_time": 39060,
        "text": "many surgeries would be \nway too traumatic to perform."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 39060,
        "end_time": 42397,
        "text": "Ancient medical texts from Egypt,\nAsia and the Middle East"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 42397,
        "end_time": 44810,
        "text": "all describe early anesthetics"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 44810,
        "end_time": 46927,
        "text": "containing things like opium poppy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 46927,
        "end_time": 48309,
        "text": "mandrake fruit,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 48309,
        "end_time": 49977,
        "text": "and alcohol."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 49977,
        "end_time": 52188,
        "text": "Today, anesthesiologists often combine"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 52188,
        "end_time": 56142,
        "text": "regional, inhalational \nand intravenous agents"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 56142,
        "end_time": 58831,
        "text": "to get the right balance for a surgery."
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 58831,
        "end_time": 63111,
        "text": "Regional anesthesia blocks pain signals\nfrom a specific part of the body"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 63111,
        "end_time": 64908,
        "text": "from getting to the brain."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 64908,
        "end_time": 70139,
        "text": "Pain and other messages travel through\nthe nervous system as electrical impulses."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 70139,
        "end_time": 74388,
        "text": "Regional anesthetics work by setting up\nan electrical barricade."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 74388,
        "end_time": 78271,
        "text": "They bind to the proteins \nin neurons&#39; cell membranes"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 78271,
        "end_time": 80906,
        "text": "that let charged particles in and out,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 80906,
        "end_time": 83987,
        "text": "and lock out positively charged particles."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 83987,
        "end_time": 86973,
        "text": "One compound that does this is cocaine,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 86973,
        "end_time": 89896,
        "text": "whose painkilling effects \nwere discovered by accident"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 89896,
        "end_time": 93999,
        "text": "when an ophthalmology intern\ngot some on his tongue."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 93999,
        "end_time": 97021,
        "text": "It&#39;s still occasionally used \nas an anesthetic,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 97021,
        "end_time": 99430,
        "text": "but many of the more common\nregional anesthetics"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 99430,
        "end_time": 103351,
        "text": "have a similar chemical structure\nand work the same way."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 103351,
        "end_time": 106180,
        "text": "But for major surgeries where you need\nto be unconscious,"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 106180,
        "end_time": 109483,
        "text": "you&#39;ll want something that acts\non the entire nervous system,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 109483,
        "end_time": 111316,
        "text": "including the brain."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 111316,
        "end_time": 114070,
        "text": "That&#39;s what inhalational anesthetics do."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 114070,
        "end_time": 118594,
        "text": "In Western medicine, diethyl ether\nwas the first common one."
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 118594,
        "end_time": 121384,
        "text": "It was best known as a recreational drug"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 121384,
        "end_time": 125464,
        "text": "until doctors started to realize that\npeople sometimes didn&#39;t notice"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 125464,
        "end_time": 128298,
        "text": "injuries they received \nunder the influence."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 128298,
        "end_time": 132444,
        "text": "In the 1840s, they started sedating\npatients with ether"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 132444,
        "end_time": 135332,
        "text": "during dental extractions and surgeries."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 135332,
        "end_time": 139149,
        "text": "Nitrous oxide became popular\nin the decades that followed"
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 139149,
        "end_time": 140826,
        "text": "and is still used today."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 140826,
        "end_time": 145007,
        "text": "although ether derivatives, \nlike sevoflurane, are more common."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 145007,
        "end_time": 150138,
        "text": "Inhalational anesthesia is usually \nsupplemented with intravenous anesthesia,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 150138,
        "end_time": 152996,
        "text": "which was developed in the 1870s."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 152996,
        "end_time": 156150,
        "text": "Common intravenous agents include\nsedatives, like propofol,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 156150,
        "end_time": 157884,
        "text": "which induce unconsciousness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 157884,
        "end_time": 162188,
        "text": "and opioids, like fentanyl, \nwhich reduce pain."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 162188,
        "end_time": 164836,
        "text": "These general anesthetics \nalso seem to work"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 164836,
        "end_time": 167907,
        "text": "by affecting electrical signals\nin the nervous system."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 167907,
        "end_time": 171754,
        "text": "Normally, the brain&#39;s electrical signals\nare a chaotic chorus"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 171754,
        "end_time": 175126,
        "text": "as different parts of the brain\ncommunicate with each other."
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 175126,
        "end_time": 178693,
        "text": "That connectivity keeps you awake\nand aware."
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 178693,
        "end_time": 180426,
        "text": "But as someone becomes anesthetized,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 180426,
        "end_time": 183549,
        "text": "those signals become calmer\nand more organized,"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 183549,
        "end_time": 185657,
        "text": "suggesting that different \nparts of the brain"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 185657,
        "end_time": 188164,
        "text": "aren&#39;t talking to each other anymore."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 188164,
        "end_time": 192800,
        "text": "There&#39;s a lot we still don&#39;t know\nabout exactly how this happens."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 192800,
        "end_time": 198771,
        "text": "Several common anesthetics bind to\nthe GABA-A receptor in the brain&#39;s neurons."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 198771,
        "end_time": 200598,
        "text": "They hold the gateway open,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 200598,
        "end_time": 205030,
        "text": "letting negatively charged particles\nflow into the cell."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 205030,
        "end_time": 208241,
        "text": "Negative charge builds up\nand acts like a log jam,"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 208241,
        "end_time": 211842,
        "text": "keeping the neuron from transmitting\nelectrical signals."
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 211842,
        "end_time": 215444,
        "text": "The nervous system has lots\nof these gated channels,"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 215444,
        "end_time": 217349,
        "text": "controlling pathways for movement,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 217349,
        "end_time": 218419,
        "text": "memory,"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 218419,
        "end_time": 219779,
        "text": "and consciousness."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 219779,
        "end_time": 222864,
        "text": "Most anesthetics probably \nact on more than one,"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 222864,
        "end_time": 225276,
        "text": "and they don&#39;t act on \njust the nervous system."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 225276,
        "end_time": 227461,
        "text": "Many anesthetics also affect the heart,"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 227461,
        "end_time": 228386,
        "text": "lungs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 228386,
        "end_time": 230417,
        "text": "and other vital organs."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 230417,
        "end_time": 232022,
        "text": "Just like early anesthetics,"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 232022,
        "end_time": 235586,
        "text": "which included familiar poisons like\nhemlock and aconite,"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 235586,
        "end_time": 238155,
        "text": "modern drugs can \nhave serious side effects."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 238155,
        "end_time": 242298,
        "text": "So an anesthesiologist has to mix\njust the right balance of drugs"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 242298,
        "end_time": 244997,
        "text": "to create all the features of anesthesia,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 244997,
        "end_time": 248019,
        "text": "while carefully monitoring\nthe patient&#39;s vital signs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 248019,
        "end_time": 250876,
        "text": "and adjusting the drug mixture as needed."
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 250876,
        "end_time": 253031,
        "text": "Anesthesia is complicated,"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 253031,
        "end_time": 254607,
        "text": "but figuring out how to use it"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 254607,
        "end_time": 258849,
        "text": "allowed for the development \nof new and better surgical techniques."
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 258849,
        "end_time": 263460,
        "text": "Surgeons could learn how to routinely\nand safely perform C-sections,"
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 263460,
        "end_time": 265167,
        "text": "reopen blocked arteries,"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 265167,
        "end_time": 267550,
        "text": "replace damaged livers and kidneys,"
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 267550,
        "end_time": 270407,
        "text": "and many other life-saving operations."
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 270407,
        "end_time": 273970,
        "text": "And each year, new anesthesia techniques\nare developed"
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 273970,
        "end_time": 278496,
        "text": "that will ensure more and more patients\nsurvive the trauma of surgery."
    }
]